    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who hoard wealth and are avaricious, grasping, stingy, and parsimonious; in the original meaning, such people live miserably in order to hoard wealth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
